End Process

Process called "openbsd_arm64_syscall_6" takes syscall_number as Integer, arg1 as Integer, arg2 as Integer, arg3 as Integer, arg4 as Integer, arg5 as Integer, arg6 as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: OpenBSD ARM64 syscall with 6 arguments
    Let result be 0
    Inline Assembly:
